channel.title: OSO source(People know from mopar toplist)
channel.description:
Base: PI
It was leaked so I just release.. I might post pictures later.
Credits:
Sanity Brandyn Me
Download: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?1jjujrnwnkf]backup.rar[/url] Use slashcape client(Add warrior maps to it.)
To add buy 50 in client add this(You shoud know where): [code] if(rsInterface.parentID == 3824) rsInterface.actions[4] = "Buy 50";[/code]
Some info:
- 99% warriors guild - Fixed all known dupes(We had around 400 online and none seem to know any more dupes) - Made it lots more stable - Added buy 50(You have to do it client sided not going to spoon feed. - 100% tele tabs - 100% obelisks + emotes - Fixed teleport timer(gfx go on good time now) - Tutorial island with questions asked(need client for it to, just remembered I might post client soon) - Lots more I post if I rember them - Added all good level reqs for all items(Also all skillcapes) - All skillcape emote + gfs work
